{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~pazzani/Slides/MLC94/sld014.htm", "content": "\r\n<!--  Presentation generated by Internet Assistant for Microsoft PowerPoint 97 -->\r\n\r\n<HTML>\r\n<HEAD>\r\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Context-Type\" CONTEXT=\"text/html;charset=windows-1252\">\r\n<meta name=\"GENERATOR\" content=\"Microsoft Internet Assistant for Microsoft PowerPoint 97\">\r\n <TITLE>Reduced Cost Ordering:</TITLE> \r\n</HEAD>\r\n\r\n<BODY     >\r\n\r\n<CENTER>\r\n<TABLE WIDTH=100%> \r\n     <TR> <TD WIDTH=100% ALIGN=CENTER>\r\n         <IMG SRC=\"img014.GIF\" usemap=\"#Objmap\" WIDTH=640 HEIGHT=480 BORDER=0>\r\n     </TD> </TR>\r\n     <TR> <TD WIDTH=100% ALIGN=CENTER>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld001.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"first.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"First\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld013.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"prev.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Previous\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld015.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"next.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Next\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"sld025.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"last.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Last\"></A>\r\n         <IMG SRC=\"space.gif\" BORDER=0>\r\n         <A HREF=\"index.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"info.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Index\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"http://www.ics.uci.edu/~pazzani\"><IMG SRC=\"home.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Home\"></A>\r\n         <A HREF=\"tsld014.htm\"><IMG SRC=\"text.gif\" BORDER=0 ALT=\"Text\"></A>\r\n     </TD> </TR>\r\n</TABLE>\r\n<P>Slide 14 of 25</P>\r\n</CENTER>\r\n<!-- <UL>\r\n<H2>Reduced Cost Ordering:\u000bPostprocessor for FOCL</H2>\r\n<BR></UL></P>\r\n<P><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Input\r\n</H2>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>n  sets of clauses (one per class)\r\n<LI>classified examples (distinct from examples used to create clauses)\r\n<LI>Cost matrix\r\n</UL></UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Output\r\n</H2>\r\n<UL>\r\n<LI>Ordered decision list using subset of the clauses\r\n<LI>default rule\r\n</UL></UL><UL>\r\n<LI><H2>Approach:</H2>\r\n</UL></P>\r\n<P><UL>\r\n1. Let Pool = an unordered set of rules learned on training set\r\n<BR></UL><UL>\r\n2. Initialize Rules to a default (Least Expected Cost Class)\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n3. Add single rule (and new default) to Rules that most \r\n</UL><UL>\r\n   lowers misclassification cost on ordering set.\r\n</UL><UL>\r\n4. Repeat until addition wouldn\u2019t lower misclassification cost.</UL></P>\r\n<P>  -->\r\n</Body>\r\n</HTML>\r\n", "encoding": "Windows-1252"}